name: Ode To Tezos (single) cover art
description:
This artwork is a derivative of QueenEarth’s original album art Introducing QueenEarth, created in 2010. In 2021 was used as the base for this cover art of the NFT release Introducing QueenEarth 2.0. This edition was created by Gevik Nalbandian for the single, “Ode to Tezos”  in the style of his original Kalamint collection, Digital Series 3. 

From QueenEarth

The original QueenEarth artwork for Introducing QueenEarth was released in 2010, always showing the Middle Passage, the waters of the Atlantic that carried Black human cargo to the Caribbean and the Americas for free labor to build the foundations of a new empire. As we traverse this Earth, may we, and the Diasporas, always find love and a home.
